This paper discusses challenges related to web archiving, replaying archived web resources, and verifying their authenticity. These topics are relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including digital libraries (cs.DL), cryptography and security (cs.CR), web technologies (cs.WEB), information retrieval (cs.IR), and software engineering (cs.SE). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
